title: Kasabian - Sex, Shrooms And Rock 'N Roll
description:
A rare live cd from 2005 by Kasabian.

Songs 1-10 were recorded at Glastonbury, 2005. 11 was recorded at BBC Radio 1 in 2004, 12 was recorded at Canal+ Paris in 2005 and 13 was recorded at Oxegen Festival in Ireland, 2005.

2. I.D.
